				<DIV>Yesterday we did the Lavaspinner's Local's&nbsp;mission for the dark reign for the second time.&nbsp; We "won," and I was the one who zoned out to complete the mission.&nbsp; I received my crystals (but no message), but I did not receive a token on my cursor.&nbsp; Everyone else received both crystals and token when I zoned out.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>In short, don't be the one who zones if you want to make sure you get a faction token.&nbsp; I did /bug this ingame, and /petitioned as well, but CS said that they are not giving out any tokens or crystals to anyone.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Just wanted to let you all know this problem.&nbsp; This is frustrating since we also "lost" the first time we ran this mission due to not being able to find the right exit with 2 hours left.&nbsp; It's no fun to be bummed about a new expansion.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>- Xulan</DIV>
